description._content: Catalog #: 09_01587 Title: Elwyn H. Gibbon Special Collection Photo Karachi India Additional Information: Elwyn Gibbon's grave at Karachi, India. ""Eldwyn"" is misspelled. Date is also incorrect. Should have been August 19, 1942, Elwyn Gibbon (b.1911 d.1942) was an American pilot who served as a pilot in the Chinese Air Force in the Foreign Volunteer Squadron. Later he served as a Vultee Aircraft Company test pilot in Karachi, India, where he died in a plane crash in 1942. Tags: Elwyn H.
